channel.title: Titan's Extreme Client
channel.description:
[center][img]http://i263.photobucket.com/albums/ii159/dream2xtreme22/titan.gif[/img][/center]
Well, I've been working on a client for a few days now.
[u][b]Features & things im working on:[/b][/u]
[ul][li]done[/li] [li]almost[/li] [li]not done[/ul]
[hr]
[ul][li]Remove useless and unwanted models[/li] [li]Ip changer that opens on loading[/li] [li]working Lunar[/li] [li]System that updates the client when a newer version is released[/li] [li]Saradomin sword gfx[/li] [li]All godsword Gfx[/li] [li]Remove all glitches[/li] [li]switch cache statement[/li] [li]Fully working prayer[/li] [li]Custom mod & admin crowns[/li] [li]Themes on Jframe[/li][/ul]
Those are my goals of completing right now.(List will be updated)
[u][b]Client picture:[/b][/u]
[img]http://i263.photobucket.com/albums/ii159/dream2xtreme22/titanextreme.jpg[/img]
[u][b]Popup Ip Changer:[/b][/u]
[img]http://i263.photobucket.com/albums/ii159/dream2xtreme22/ipchanger.jpg[/img]
[u][b]Prayer Pictures:[/b][/u]
[img]http://i263.photobucket.com/albums/ii159/dream2xtreme22/allprayers.jpg[/img]
[u][b]Video:[/b][/u] [url=http://s263.photobucket.com/albums/ii159/dream2xtreme22/?action=view&current=Client.flv]Click Here[/url]
[u][b]Known Glitches:[/b][/u]
*When i added the Protect from melee spirite it dissapeared, and now it appears as a skull - Will be fixed
*the Mapback was a little too small so you can see around the edges a little - Will be fixed
